script = ExtResource("1_pfurf")
questions = Array[String](["How have you kept at being a leader for so long?", "What do you know about the other settlements?", "What’s with all the windmills?", "What’s Breezekiln like?"])
answers = Array[String](["Because no one else wanted the job. And I didn’t trust anyone else to do it right. Simple as that.", "I know enough. They’ve got their own ways, we’ve got ours. Some more organized than us, some less so. A few of ‘em keep to themselves, and I get why. There’s no perfect place left, so everyone makes do. We work. They work. That’s all the similarity that matters.", "They’re what keep us breathin’. Rebuilt 'em myself after the duct system burned out two cycles back. No help. Just metal, sweat, and time. It’s my paradise. They may be loud, but they work. That’s what matters.", "Hot. Loud. Always on the edge of failing. But folks here don’t quit. It’s not for everyone. But if you’ve got a good pair of boots and a head that stays down, you’ll get by."])
