script = ExtResource("1_6w2tb")
npc_name = "Garrick"
initial_dialog = "You’re the Spiritkeeper, right? I’ve heard about you. Garrick Ironwhistle. I keep Breezekiln in one piece. Most days.
Nice to meet you. What’s happening here?
Repairs. Maintenance. Same thing every day. Something breaks, I fix it. Lately, it’s been more breakin’ than fixin’.
Do you need my help?
Yeah. Don’t expect me to roll out a welcome mat, but I can’t do it all myself no more. If you’re stickin’ around, make yourself useful. You’ll figure where you fit. If you pull your weight, I’ll make it worth your while.
"
alternative_dialog = SubResource("Resource_3dl0e")
